data.description: Charming 3 bed, 2 1/2 bath in quiet cul-de-sac near walking trail and park. Enjoy the custom details & finished basement (2019) in this updated home. Custom entertainment center with flat screen TV and fireplace remains with home. Relax while you enjoy the incredible landscaping, orchard, raised garden beds & grape vines. Your private oasis includes an outdoor kitchen, fireplace, privacy fence, storage shed & koi pond. Newer roof, triple pane windows and A/C. Don't miss out on this home!
